{"type": "article", "id": 27027, "title": "水泥家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-19T07:13:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145409BXtarLe2d79yoJWm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>作为 <a href=\"http://www.fernandomastrangelo.com/\">Fernando Mastrangelo</a> 推出的 MMATERIAL 线的新品，Fade 是一系列有着细腻彩色层次的家具，看上去好像是将一幅幅抽象画给具象的成果。通过手工染色和逐层浇筑的方式，Mastrangelo 成功地让水泥能够呈现出水墨般渲染的效果， 打造出了这些吸引人眼球的家具表面，可以说是一次艺术与设计的完美结合。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145407VTAOu2nUYD4kqyQC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.27754237\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145408Qaj8NBIlWKoFJ2CE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09895833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145408xyGADBZju61dSEr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145409UHk0efdFqnVOwRWZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99895833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}